{"tid":1515134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美媒指司法部擬以國安為由　反對開通連接香港光纖電纜","createTime":"2019-08-29T04:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:33:51.000Z","uid":11148,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b8097c6151598d17b713220ee6564e9502b61692","tid":1515134,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"美國《華爾街日報》報道，美國司法部可能以國家安全為理由，反對開通一條連接美國洛杉磯至香港的海底光纖電纜。<br />\n<br />\n報道表示，由Google、Facebook及中國第四大電訊營運商的鵬博士電訊傳媒集團，合作鋪設這條跨太平洋的海底電纜，鋪設工程至今已完成了大半，完成後需要取得商業經營許可才能開始營運，但報道引述消息人士表示，美國司法部基於國家安全上的顧慮，當中有中國電訊傳媒集團，以及電纜在香港容易受中國控制，反對這條光纖網絡營運。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部國安事務發言人表示，外商投資或取得股權的申請個案，若果涉及國家安全和執法顧慮，美國聯邦傳播委員會會轉介司法部，司法部目前不作評論。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477430-20190829.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477430-20190829.htm&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=2a27a385\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477430-20190829.htm&h=82a5173c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477430-20190829.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n條電纜支那好似出左幾多錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝林奠,攬炒go <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570fb73ad2256126be0bbbbf250879353676e96f","tid":1515134,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"起完冇錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bddbf300c40220c7b72cfb8e2b46cf18dbacf8","tid":1515134,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"htt